values:
And Here We Have Another National  Writing Novel Month Writing Journal. Pleased To Meet You! Here's a little on the owner (and writer) of this journal. ((this quiz was taken from the questionnaire posted over at , so I don't take any credit for writing it.))

Name/Nickname: Joanna, Jojobeans, Jojo (most commonly used) and Soanna.
Name on the NaNo site: thefinalsky (how lame am I?)
Age: 16 (D: so young...not)
Location: Southern California. The Inland Empire, if you must know.
How many years involved in NaNoWriMo: None, before this. This is my first year writing for NaNoWriMo, but I've written things like this before. Only 20,000 words less. :O
How many won: None! But I plan on trying really hard to finish. I like the idea.
This year's genre: fantasy, more than likely.
This year's story idea, if you have one: not entirely sure. There are a few floating around in my head though.
Word wars?: Sure! Makes things go faster, if you ask me. XD
Favorite character in KH: Believe it or not, Kairi. She's such a great character, I think. Never gets enough love, and is always considered the separation between Riku and Sora's smex love. I love Riku and Sora too though. And Roxas. And Olette. And Axel. -shot-
Any other fandoms that you love?: The Final Fantasies, most notably FFVII, because I love Zack and Cloud. Ouran High School Host Club. Harry Potter. Twilight.
About you in general: just go read my profile. But hmmm...I want to be a psychology major when I get to college? Heh. But I'm rather mature, i guess...no matter how much what I do contradicts that statement. And I love green. XD
Anything else?: BRING ON THE CHALLENGE! :D
